Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.25,0:40:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一颗暗红的恒星已经进入了奥尔特云{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}A dark-reddish star has entered the Oort Cloud.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.61,0:40:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}涅墨西斯归来了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Nemesis has returned.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.47,0:40:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果人类仍在地球上生存{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If humans still exist on Earth,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.97,0:40:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们即将面临一个缓缓酝酿的宇宙威胁{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they'll face a slow-building but imminent cosmic threat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.33,0:40:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥尔特云团可能有十亿余颗彗星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The Oort Cloud contains perhaps 10 trillion comets, maybe even more.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.74,0:41:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 它相当庞大{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But remember, it's really big.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.31,0:41:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以若你置身奥尔特云团之中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So if you were in the Oort Cloud,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.42,0:41:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它不会让你时刻都被彗星撞击{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it's not like you would be pelted by comets all the time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.68,0:41:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它们之间的间距一般都很大{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The spaces between them would pretty big.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.40,0:41:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像这颗杂耍人手中的保龄球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Like a bowling ball in a juggler's hands,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.76,0:41:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}涅墨西斯只会让少数彗星轨道混乱{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Nemesis simply shuffles some comets out of its way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.24,0:41:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥尔特云团的中间有一块空旷的地方{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The Oort Cloud has an empty region in the middle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.67,0:41:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它是被木星和太阳清理干净的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's been cleaned out by Jupiter and by the Sun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.22,0:41:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们就生活在这里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We live in that region.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.70,0:41:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但随着涅墨西斯的靠近{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But as Nemesis approaches,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.60,0:41:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太阳系的内部就成了一个射击场{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the inner Solar System becomes a shooting gallery.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.20,0:41:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因此有可能会出现数量比平时稍多的彗星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And so there would start to be a few more comets than usual,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.52,0:41:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后突然 满眼望去 尽皆彗星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and then, suddenly, there are just comets, comets coming all the time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.10,0:41:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}数量最多的时 每年将有一千至一万颗彗星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And at the peak, there might be 1,000 to 10,000 comets per year in the sky.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.10,0:41:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分析显示{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}According to the projections{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.84,0:42:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地球会成为会成万箭彗星的靶心{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Earth would be in the crosshairs of this comet storm{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.17,0:42:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长达一百万年之久{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}for a million years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.24,0:42:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这一百万年中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Over a period of a million years,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.18,0:42:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能有约十亿颗彗星造访{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}there would be visits by about a billion comets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.36,0:42:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事实上 你可以算一算{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Actually, you do the calculation,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.04,0:42:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总归有一颗会撞上地球 或者两颗{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it turns out one of them will hit the Earth. One or two.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.32,0:42:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很难准确预言{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It'd be difficult to predict exactly{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.56,0:42:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它究竟会在何时发生{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}when the impact would happen,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.33,0:42:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过可能会有这么个阶段{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but there would be this phase...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.88,0:42:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是一段危险的时间{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This sort of danger zone in which the chances{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.93,0:42:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在此期间 彗星撞击地球的几率{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}for a catastrophic impact with something of a comet's size{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.24,0:42:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要比现在高很多{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}would be much, much higher than they are now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.81,0:42:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这次冲撞会再次引发地球物种覆灭吗{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Will the impact spark another catastrophic extinction on Earth?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.32,0:42:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有可能{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Perhaps.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.51,0:42:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除非人类坐以待毙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But only if we let it happen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.02,0:42:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我喜欢开玩笑说涅墨西斯这次失算了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}I like to joke that Nemesis planned this one poorly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.46,0:42:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们处于上次大灭绝与下次之间{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In between the last extinction and the next one,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.77,0:43:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}高智能的生物有大把的时间集中精力{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}there's plenty of time for intelligent life to get its act together{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.22,0:43:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}确保涅墨西斯再次归来时{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to make sure that next time Nemesis comes back{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.49,0:43:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽天空彗星满布{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and the sky is filled with comets,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.96,0:43:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}却都不会撞击地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to make sure that none of them hit us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.72,0:43:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}覆灭之路是无法避免的吗{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Is this future inevitable?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.86,0:43:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除非科学家们找到涅墨西斯{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Until scientists either discover Nemesis{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.39,0:43:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或完全否认其存在{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}or definitively rule it out,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.33,0:43:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没人能够确定{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}no one can know for sure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.99,0:43:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要知道这不仅仅只是一次抽象的假设{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's important to realize this is not just an abstract discussion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.31,0:43:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些物体撞击地球无疑是小几率事件{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Clearly, these objects colliding with Earth happen very rarely.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.78,0:43:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但换个角度来说 当它们真的撞上来了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But on the other hand, when they do collide,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.68,0:43:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它们带来的冲击是巨大的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}they're extremely cataclysmic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.58,0:43:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我们能做的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So what we need to be able to do{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.86,0:43:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是要更进一步的了解太阳系{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}is get better understanding of our Solar System,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.10,0:43:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并密切留意我们的天空{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and keep an eye on the sky,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.60,0:43:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为它可能会是决定我们生死的关键{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}because it maybe crucial for our survival.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.08,0:43:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果未来有一天 真的彗星漫天{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If the future sky one day does fill with comets,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.68,0:43:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类也许会找到一条自救之路{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}perhaps humanity will have found a way to save itself{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.11,0:43:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而非最终成为太阳邪恶双子星的又一牺牲品{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}rather than end up one more victim of the Sun's evil twin.{\r}
